FRONT LOT, ANIMATION COURTYARD, PRODUCTION

COURTYARD AND BACKLOT. THESE AREAS EACH INCLUDE THEMED RIDES,

ATTRACTIONS, SHOWS, RESTAURANTS, MERCHANDISE SHOPS AND

