DEVELOPMENT OF THE SITE ALSO CONTINUES WITH THE

VAL DEUROPE PROJECT, A NEWLY CONSTRUCTED PLANNED COMMUNITY

BEING BUILT NEAR DISNEYLAND RESORT PARIS. THE FIRST TWO PHASES

