GAMES WORLDWIDE. BVG ALSO LICENSES PROPERTIES AND WORKS DIRECTLY

WITH THIRD-PARTY INTERACTIVE GAME PUBLISHERS TO BRING PRODUCTS

TO MARKET. BVG PRIMARILY FOCUSES ON MULTI-PLATFORM

